Hi, there! I graduated with a Masters degree in Computer Science this March. I am passionate about software development, creating UIs that tell a story. I have explored and worked with many technologies and frameworks as part of my learning curve and now use Java, Javascript, CSS, HTML, jQuery, AngularJS, Ruby and BootStrap to create programmable solutions. I was responsible for developing responsive and cross browser compatible widgets and deploying them into major e-commerce client websites. This work experience gave me a good exposure of full stack software engineering and helped me hone my skills. Currently, I'm looking for full time opportunities as Software Engineer/Web developer.
